Four warm cats, five frozen dogs.
(Jersey: Quat' caûds cats, chînq tchians g'lés.)

The black cat's thick cheeks.
(Finnish: Mustan kissan paksut posket.)

The cat hat vomited in the kitchen cupboard.
(German: Die Chatz chat ins Chuchichäschtli chechözelet.)

Itty-bitty cats vomit itty-bitty vomit. Itty-bitty vomit is vomited by itty-bitty cats.
(German: Klitze kleine Katzen kotzen klitze kleine Kotze. Klitze kleine Kotze kotzen klitze kleine Katzen.)

His cat sings his song.
(French: Son chat chante sa chanson.)





The Cat saw the roast. The roast tempted the cat. The cat put a paw on the roast. The roast burned the paw of the cat. The cat left the roast.
(French: Chat vit rôtrôt tenta chatchat mit patte à rôtrôt brûla patte à chatchat quitta rôt.)
